hopobject.body: What sort of music do you like? myhealthpick.com Smith, a 6-6 guard, is still on the mend after having surgery on his left knee in July and has yet to start running in practice. But along with repairing his body, Smith must also restore his relationship with Woodson, which helped Smith to his best season yet. Yet Smith has a way of making things hard on himself, and he seemed to struggle with his shooting in the playoffs after the one-game ban.
